  <original-body>This will allow the values of collection/member hashes within a resource definition to be arrays of symbols. This is an alternative to supplying :any if a particular action needs, for instance, to be able to respond to a GET or POST request.

@@@ ruby
map.resources :messages, :collection =&gt; { :search =&gt; [:get, :post] }
@@@</original-body>
